Is the Object Empty?
Write a function that returns true if an object is empty, and false otherwise.

Examples
isEmpty({}) ➞ true

isEmpty({ a: 1 }) ➞ false

https://edabit.com/challenge/nGybgqB9agSqvBszF

My Solution

function isEmpty(obj) {
	let value = 0
	for (const property in obj){
		value = property
	}
	if (value === 0) {
		return true
	}
	return false
}
